@startuml
[*] --> PendingStudent
PendingStudent --> ActiveStudent : enroll in active class
ActiveStudent --> Enrolled : active enrollment exists
Enrolled --> Transferring : teacher transfers class
Transferring --> PreviousEnrollmentClosed : set unenrolled_at
PreviousEnrollmentClosed --> Enrolled : create next enrollment
Enrolled --> JoiningClassGuild : Discord identity + class guild exist
JoiningClassGuild --> Enrolled : add guild member succeeds or is skipped
Enrolled --> Withdrawn : withdraw from class
Withdrawn --> Enrolled : reinstate/enroll again
PendingStudent --> Archived : archive pending student
Enrolled --> Archived : archive student
Archived --> ActiveStudent : reinstate
@enduml
